      "content": "i know i should talk to someone but i'm just tired of the cycle. it's like every time i try to \"cope\" i'm just delaying the inevitable. it honestly feels like some people are just meant to suffer and there is no point in fighting it anymore. isn't there a certain kind of peace in just accepting that it's over?",
